text: Sander van der Marck (born 20 December 1972) is a Dutch rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Delft
